ican Party]]<ref>{{cite news|url=https://www.politicspa.com/pagop-unanimously-endorses-president-trump-at-fall-meeting/92341/|title=PAGOP Unanimously Endorses President Trump at Fall Meeting|work=PoliticsPA|author=John Cole|date=September 23, 2019|accessdate=September 28, 2019}}</ref>\n\n===Organizations===\n* [[Committee to Defend the President]]<ref name=\"TrumpPACs\">{{cite web|url=https://www.publicintegrity.org/2017/05/05/20832/pro-trump-super-pacs-have-already-spent-1-million-election-2020|title=Pro-Trump super PACs have already spent $1 million on Election 2020|date=May 5, 2017|first=Dave|last=Levinthal|work=[[Center for Public Integrity]]|accessdate=May 6, 2017}}</ref>\n* [[Great America Committee]]<ref>{{cite web|url=https://www.nbcnews.com/politics/white-house/pence-creates-pac-ahead-2018-2020-elections-n761436|title=Pence Creates PAC Ahead of 2018, 2020 Elections|date=May 18, 2017|first=Vaughn|last=Hillyard|work=[[NBC News]]|accessdate=May 18, 2017}}</ref>\n* [[Great America PAC]]<ref name=TrumpPACs/>\n* [[National Right to Life Committee]]<ref>{{cite web|url=https://www.nationalrighttolifenews.org/2019/07/national-right-to-life-endorses-president-trump-for-re-election/|title=National Right to Life Endorses President Trump for Re-Election|work=National Right to Life News|date=July 4, 2019|accessdate=July 13, 2019}}</ref>\n* [[Log Cabin Republicans]]<ref>{{cite web|url=https://www.washingtonpost.com/opinions/trump-met-his-commitments-to-lgbtq-americans-he-has-our-endorsement/2019/08/15/fb9b741c-bf96-11e9-a5c6-1e74f7ec4a93_story.html|title=Trump met his commitments to LGBTQ Americans. He has our endorsement.|work=[[The Washington Post]]|last2=Homan|first2=Jill|last1=Kabel|first1=Robert|date=August 15, 2019|accessdate=August 16, 2019}}</ref>\n* [[International Union of Police Associations]]<ref>{{cite web|url=https://www.courthousenews.com/police-union-backs-trump-for-re-election-in-2020/|title=Police Union Backs Trump for Re-Election in 2020|work=[[Courthou