83/|title=Christie\u2019s Scathing Indictment of Trump|first=Conor|last=Friedersdorf|date=June 25, 2019|website=The Atlantic}}</ref>\n* [[Scott Walker (politician)|Scott Walker]], [[Governor of Wisconsin|Governor]] of [[Wisconsin]] 2011\u20132019, [[Scott Walker 2016 presidential campaign|candidate]] for President in [[Republican Party presidential primaries, 2016|2016]]<ref>{{cite web |last1=Vetterkind |first1=Riley |title=Scott Walker says he will chair Trump's Wisconsin re-election campaign |url=https://madison.com/wsj/news/local/govt-and-politics/scott-walker-says-he-will-chair-trump-s-wisconsin-re/article_01cf8d2c-93e9-5fa3-b0bb-44508c85d598.html |website=madison.com |accessdate=1 March 2020 |language=en}}</ref>\n\n===Statewide officials===\n====Current====\n* [[Jeanette N\u00fa\u00f1ez]], [[Lieutenant Governor of Florida|Lieutenant Governor]] of [[Florida]] 2019\u2013present<ref name=ltndt>{{cite web|url=https://blog.4president.org/2020/2019/06/trump-campaign-announces-launch-of-latinos-for-trump-ahead-of-the-2020-election-.html|title=Trump Campaign Announces Launch of 'Latinos for Trump' Ahead of the 2020 Election|work=2020 Presidential Campaign Blog|date=June 25, 2019|accessdate=August 6, 2019}}</ref>\n* [[George P. Bush]], [[Texas General Land Office|Land Commissioner]] of [[Texas]] 2015\u2013present<ref>{{cite news |url=https://www.nbcnews.com/card/george-p-bush-sticks-trump-rocky-reelection-bid-n853641 |title=George P. Bush sticks with Trump in re-election bid |work=[[NBC News]] |date=March 5, 2018 |accessdate=April 11, 2019}}</ref>\n\n====Former====\n* [[Adam Putnam]], [[Florida Commissioner of Agriculture|Commissioner of Agriculture]] of [[Florida]] 2011\u20132019; [[United States House of Representatives|U.S. Representative]] from [[Florida's 12th congressional district|FL-12]] 2001\u20132011; candidate for [[List of Governors of Florida|Governor]] in [[2018 Florida gubernatorial election|2018]]<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.tampabay.com/florida-politi